msgctxt "seo_title"
msgid "Blog - Mozilla Foundation"
msgstr "Blog – Mozilla Foundation"

msgctxt "search_description"
msgid "Mozilla’s blog features guides to making your online life better, stories from the movement, and critical analysis of issues around internet health."
msgstr "De blog van Mozilla bevat handleidingen om uw online leven te verbeteren, verhalen uit de beweging en kritische analyse van problemen rond internetgezondheid."

